<i>noun</i>: 회피 [회피/훼피], 외면 [외ː면/웨ː면] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>회피 [회피/훼피]</dt><br>
<dd>1. avoidance; evasion</dd><br>
<dd>만나지 않고 피함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of avoiding someone without meeting him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. avoidance; evasion; buck-passing</dd><br>
<dd>책임을 지지 않고 피함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of avoiding taking responsibility for something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. avoidance; evasion; dodging</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 일을 하기 싫어서 나서지 않고 피함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of disliking and avoiding doing a certain task.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>외면 [외ː면/웨ː면]</dt><br>
<dd>1. looking away; turning away</dd><br>
<dd>마주치기를 원하지 않아서 얼굴을 돌려 피함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of turning away one's face in order not to see someone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. avoidance; disregard</dd><br>
<dd>현실, 사실, 진리 등을 인정하지 않고 무시함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of ignoring a fact, reality, truth, etc., without accepting it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>